{"id":23,"parent_id":0,"book_id":22911,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":23,"title":"Why is Jesus Christ so important to us?","subtitle":"By Elder Dallin H. Oaks","short_title":"Why is Jesus Christ so important to us?","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"article","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.head1"},[".seriesTitle","Special Witness"],[".title","Why is Jesus Christ so important to us?"],[".byline",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.p3"},"By Elder Dallin H. Oaks"],["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.p4"},"Of the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles"]],[".event",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.p5"},"From “Teachings of Jesus,”",["span.emphasis","Liahona"],"and",["span.emphasis","Ensign,"],"Nov. 2011, 90–91, 93."]],["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/leaders/dallin-h-oaks.jpg"}],[".kicker","The members of the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles are special witnesses of Jesus Christ."]],[".bodyBlock",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.p7"},"He is our Creator."],["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.p8"},"He gave priesthood power to His Apostles and to others."],["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.p9"},"His teachings light our path and show us the way back to Heavenly Father."],["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.p10"},"The Atonement of Jesus Christ gives us the opportunity to have the blessings of eternal life."],["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.p11"},"Through His Resurrection, we will live again."],["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.p12"},"This is the most important knowledge on earth. The Holy Ghost has revealed it to me, and He will reveal it to you."],[".figure",{"id":"f1","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/leaders/fr13mar17-why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-2013-02-05.jpg"}],[".credit",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/liahona/2013/03/why-is-jesus-christ-so-important-to-us.p13"},"Clockwise from the top: detail from",["span.emphasis","Christ Creating the Earth,"],"by Robert T. Barrett © 1996; detail from",["span.emphasis","Christ Ordaining the Twelve Apostles,"],"by Harry Anderson © IRI; detail from",["span.emphasis","The Second Coming,"],"by Harry Anderson © IRI; detail from",["span.emphasis","Christ with the Children,"],"by Harry Anderson © IRI"]]]]]]],"refs":null}
